Enum APMaterial

All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<APMaterial>
public enum APMaterial
extends java.lang.Enum<APMaterial>

Materials for APSim. This enum contains identities for many different materials. Buoyancy is defined as being a gas. Constructor format: MATERIAL(byte[24] color, boolean isBuoyant, boolean isLiquid, boolean unused, float flowChance, short ID, int density, String name); NOTE: 1-Gas 2-Liquid 3-Normal Solid 4-Dense Solid/Liquid
